{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6cd3343fda","title":"《反对本本主义》说明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e7d4f18235","index":0,"year":1961,"month":3,"day":11,"articleId":"6cd3343fda"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wansui5","name":"毛泽东思想万岁(1961-1968卷)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"未知","files":"/books/wansui5a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wansui5":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3d3ed60757","type":"title","text":"《反对本本主义》说明","index":0,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"},{"id":"67180317ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（原名《关于调查研究》）","index":1,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"},{"id":"f5a304e6c0","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一篇老文章，是为了反对当时红军中的教条主义思想而写的。那时没有用“教条主义”这个名称，我们叫它做“本本主义”。写作时间大约在一九三零年春季，已经三十年不见了。一九六一年一月，忽然从中央革命博物馆里找到。","index":2,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"},{"id":"e894c83c15","type":"paragraph","text":"而中央革命博物馆是从福建龙岩地找到的。看来还有些用处。印若干分供同志们参考。","index":3,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"},{"id":"9eb66e9e12","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"},{"id":"348a6307aa","type":"subdate","text":"一九六一年三月十一日","index":5,"publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda"}],"page":{"id":"3f803b7a31","publicationId":"wansui5","articleId":"6cd3343fda","start":27,"end":27}}}},"__N_SSG":true}